  "config": {
    "title": "CamelotScavengerFixed",
    "details": "A medieval Camelot-themed DApp for the CamelotScavengerFixed ERC20 token contract. Features:\n1. Connect Wallet button (MetaMask or other Web3 providers)\n2. Display token name (Camelot Excalibur), symbol (EXCAL), total supply, and user balance\n3. Mint tokens using mintByMnemonic function with a text input field for the mnemonic phrase\n4. Display remaining solver pool (REMAINING_MINT - mintedBySolvers) and per-solver mint amount (PER_SOLVER_MINT)\n5. Verify Bitcoin Genesis address binding (verifyBitcoinGenesisBinding) and CREATE2 deployment (verifyCREATE2Deployment) using contract's pure functions — show results in UI\n6. Also show verifyGenesisNonceBinding result\n7. Show hasMinted status for connected wallet\n8. Medieval/Camelot theme: parchment tones (#F5E6C8, #EDD9A3), gold accents (#C9A84C, #8B6914), dark brown borders, gothic/serif fonts (MedievalSharp or Cinzel from Google Fonts), decorative dividers, shield/sword icons, scroll-like card containers, candlelight/amber glow effects on buttons\n9. Responsive layout with header showing connected wallet address and ETH balance\n10. Toast/notification system for transaction feedback",
    "description": "A medieval Camelot-themed DApp for the CamelotScavengerFixed ERC20 token contract. Features:\n1. Connect Wallet button (MetaMask or other Web3 providers)\n2. Display token name (Camelot Excalibur), symbol (EXCAL), total supply, and user balance\n3. Mint tokens using mintByMnemonic function with a text input field for the mnemonic phrase\n4. Display remaining solver pool (REMAINING_MINT - mintedBySolvers) and per-solver mint amount (PER_SOLVER_MINT)\n5. Verify Bitcoin Genesis address binding (verifyBitcoinGenesisBinding) and CREATE2 deployment (verifyCREATE2Deployment) using contract's pure functions — show results in UI\n6. Also show verifyGenesisNonceBinding result\n7. Show hasMinted status for connected wallet\n8. Medieval/Camelot theme: parchment tones (#F5E6C8, #EDD9A3), gold accents (#C9A84C, #8B6914), dark brown borders, gothic/serif fonts (MedievalSharp or Cinzel from Google Fonts), decorative dividers, shield/sword icons, scroll-like card containers, candlelight/amber glow effects on buttons\n9. Responsive layout with header showing connected wallet address and ETH balance\n10. Toast/notification system for transaction feedback",
